                "key": "The Moonring Sighted",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>For 12s after triggering a Swirl reaction, ATK increases by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">24%/30%/34%/38%/42%</span>. In addition, when 1/2 or more characters in the party are of a different Elemental Type from the equipping character, the DMG dealt by the equipping character's Charged Attacks is increased by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">20%/48%</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">25%/60% </span>| <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">30%/72% </span>| <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">35%/84% </span>| <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">40%/96% </span>and Elemental Burst DMG dealt is increased by <span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">10%/24%</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">12.5%/30% </span>| <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">15%/36% </span>| <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">17.5%/42% </span>| <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">20%/48%</span>.</p>"
                ]
              },
